channel.title: Items only spawn last 3 numbers of ID
channel.description: When I try to spawn items in my funscap3 with silab's source, it will only ever spawn the last 3 numbers of the item ID. like if I want to spawn 1052, it will spawn item 0052. If I try to spawn item 6889, it will spawn item 0889. I'm not sure what the problem is, can someone maybe copy off what they have in whatever file i need to edit for this, on funscap3 V3? Thanks.
